Frontier Tower UI/UX Design Guide for Guest Pass Form
üé® PRIMARY COLORS & THEME
Main Brand Purple

Primary Purple: rgb(118, 74, 226) or #764AE2
Secondary Purple: rgb(131, 111, 182) or #836FB6
This is their signature purple used for primary buttons and brand elements

Background Colors

Main Background: rgb(255, 255, 255) (white)
Section Backgrounds: rgb(17, 17, 17) (dark sections)
Card/Container Backgrounds: rgb(25, 25, 26) (dark containers)
Input Backgrounds: rgb(238, 238, 238) (light gray)

Text Colors

Primary Text: rgb(23, 23, 23) (near black)
Secondary Text: rgb(102, 102, 102) (medium gray)
Muted Text: rgb(136, 136, 136) (light gray)
White Text: rgb(255, 255, 255) (on dark backgrounds)

üìù TYPOGRAPHY
Primary Font Family
cssfont-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", "Plus Jakarta Sans Fallback"
Secondary Font
cssfont-family: "Outfit", "Outfit Fallback"
Font Sizes

Large Headers: 56px, 48px
Medium Headers: 36px, 32px
Sub Headers: 24px, 22px
Body Text: 16px (base size)
Small Text: 14px, 12px
Button Text: 14px with font-weight: 600

üîò BUTTON STYLES
Primary Button (Purple CTA)
cssbackground-color: rgb(118, 74, 226);
color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
padding: 10px 12px;
border-radius: 12px;
border: 1px solid rgb(235, 229, 251);
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 600;
font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", "Plus Jakarta Sans Fallback";
height: 42px;
cursor: pointer;
box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px -1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 2px 4px -2px;
transition: 0.15s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
Secondary Button (Outline/Ghost)
cssbackground-color: transparent;
color: rgb(118, 74, 226);
border: 1px solid rgb(118, 74, 226);
padding: 10px 12px;
border-radius: 12px;
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 600;
üìã INPUT FIELD STYLES
Text Input Fields
cssbackground-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);
color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
border: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255);
border-radius: 9999px; /* Fully rounded pills */
font-size: 14px;
font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", "Plus Jakarta Sans Fallback";
height: 45px;
padding: 0 16px;
box-shadow: none;
Focus States

Add subtle purple border: border-color: rgb(118, 74, 226)
Add purple box-shadow: box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(118, 74, 226, 0.1)

üì¶ CONTAINER & CARD STYLES
Main Form Container
cssbackground-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
border-radius: 24px;
box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 15px -3px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px -4px;
padding: 32px;
max-width: 600px;
margin: 0 auto;
Section Dividers
cssborder-radius: 18px;
background-color: rgb(25, 25, 26); /* For dark sections */
padding: 24px;
margin: 16px 0;
üè∑Ô∏è FORM LABELS & STRUCTURE
Form Labels
cssfont-size: 14px;
font-weight: 600;
color: rgb(23, 23, 23);
margin-bottom: 8px;
font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", "Plus Jakarta Sans Fallback";
Form Groups

Spacing between form elements: margin-bottom: 20px
Label to input spacing: margin-bottom: 8px

üéØ SPACING & LAYOUT
Standard Spacing Scale

Extra Large: 48px
Large: 32px
Medium: 24px
Small: 16px
Extra Small: 12px, 8px

Border Radius Scale

Full Rounded: 9999px (pills)
Large: 24px
Medium: 18px, 12px
Small: 2px

‚ú® SPECIAL EFFECTS & INTERACTIONS
Box Shadows

Elevated Cards: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 15px -3px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px -4px
Subtle Cards: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px -1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 2px 4px -2px
Buttons: Same as elevated cards

Hover States

Buttons: Darken purple by 10% rgb(106, 66, 203)
Subtle scale: transform: scale(1.02)
Smooth transitions: transition: all 0.15s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)

üì± RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR
Mobile Breakpoints

Desktop: 1200px+
Tablet: 768px - 1199px
Mobile: < 768px

Mobile Adjustments

Reduce padding on containers from 32px to 20px
Stack form elements vertically with 100% width
Adjust font sizes down by 2-4px
Reduce button heights from 42px to 38px

üîç FORM SPECIFIC GUIDELINES
Guest Pass Form Structure

Header Section: Clean white background with purple accent
Form Container: White card with shadow, rounded corners
Input Fields: Pill-shaped with light gray backgrounds
Submit Button: Purple CTA button, full width on mobile
Supporting Text: Medium gray color for instructions

Validation States

Error: Red border rgb(239, 68, 68), red text
Success: Green border rgb(34, 197, 94), green text
Focus: Purple border and subtle shadow

Loading States

Purple spinner or skeleton loading
Disable buttons with reduced opacity 0.6

üé® OVERALL DESIGN PHILOSOPHY
Key Characteristics

Modern & Clean: Lots of white space, minimal clutter
Tech-Forward: Sharp corners mixed with rounded elements
Professional: Sophisticated color palette
Accessible: Good contrast ratios, readable fonts
Consistent: Unified spacing and component patterns

Inspiration Keywords

Startup/Tech aesthetic
Premium SaaS application
Modern co-working space branding
Silicon Valley sophistication
Community-focused design

üí° IMPLEMENTATION NOTES

Always use the exact purple color rgb(118, 74, 226) for primary actions
Maintain the pill-shaped input aesthetic with border-radius: 9999px
Use proper font weights - 600 for buttons/labels, 400 for body text
Include hover and focus states for all interactive elements
Test on mobile - their design is mobile-first responsive
Use consistent box shadows for depth and hierarchy
Keep generous spacing between elements for breathing room

This guide captures the exact visual DNA of Frontier Tower's website. Use these specifications to create a guest pass form that seamlessly integrates with their brand aesthetic!